  ('Shoulder Prawn','King Prawn to Shoulder','7',now(),'2024-01-01','Ian Eisenberg','King Prawn to Shoulder',null,'https://www.instagram.com/p/C--bsTgiSON/','ROCKET','SHOULDER'),
  ('Spork','Cork 540 Space Orbital to Feet','9',now(),'2024-01-01','Ian Eisenberg','...',null,'https://www.instagram.com/p/DCFUuNAO2zK/','STAND','STAND'),
  ('Double Shoulder Vader',null,'9',now(),'2024-01-01','Ian Eisenberg','ShoulderVader with an additional roll.',null,'https://www.instagram.com/p/DGTgGw4sJyp/','SHOULDER','EXPOSURE'),
  ('Shoulder Frontflip','Shoulder Frontroll to Shoulder','4',now(),'2022-01-01','Sebastian Egger','From Shoulder do a Frontroll but don''t stop in Korean but keep going to land in Shoulder.',null,'https://www.instagram.com/p/Craw32qgRH3/','SHOULDER','SHOULDER'),
  ('Backbounce Spiral','360 Backbounce to Backbounce','5',now(),'2022-01-01','Sebastian Egger','From Backbounce grab the line with one hand below your back and step on the line with the opposite foot. Turn towards the chest and swap both your hands and feet to be able to finish the full rotation.',null,'https://www.instagram.com/p/CnXOzwgK3qb/','BACK','BACK'),
  ('Lasagna Flip','Hammock Backroll from Feet to Feet','9',now(),'2024-01-01','Sebastian Egger','Start with an early Hammock Roll from Feet and just when you finished the Hammock Roll part you add a Backroll to Feet.',null,'https://www.instagram.com/p/C25OqhrM8zh/','STAND','STAND'),
  ('Dislocator','Dislocate Resurrection','6',now(),'2024-01-01','Sebastian Egger','Drop to Dislocate and finish the trick like you would for a Resurrection','Make sure your shoulders are ready for it! First try it statically from Rocket, then drop in from Sofa and only when this feels safe you can start trying from feet.','https://www.instagram.com/p/C8aFBqrMHZc/','ROCKET','EXPOSURE'),
  ('Shoulder Roll Frontroll to Feet',null,'8',now(),'2024-01-01','Sebastian Egger','Start with a Shoulder Roll then add a Frontroll to Feet.',null,'https://www.instagram.com/p/C85JKKtMsy4/','SHOULDER','STAND'),
  ('FS 180 Shoulder Spin',null,'5',now(),'2024-01-01','Sebastian Egger','Spin 180 on your shoulder. You first have to regrab the far hand then to finish on the other shoulder you have to regrab the close hand (which on the other shoulder is now the far hand).',null,'https://www.instagram.com/p/C-qfaMXS70_/','SHOULDER','SHOULDER'),
  ('FS 360 Shoulder Spin',null,'7',now(),'2024-05-01','Sebastian Egger','Watch the video...',null,'https://www.instagram.com/p/C-5Bp3My3vw/','SHOULDER','SHOULDER'),
  ('360 Nevermind Roll to Feet',null,'8',now(),'2024-01-01','Sebastian Egger','Nevermind with a roll and a 360 ending in Expo.',null,'https://youtu.be/r6hcjIbrbr8?t=229','NEVERMIND','EXPOSURE'),
  ('FS 540 Nevermind',null,'8',now(),'2024-01-01','Sebastian Egger','Nevermind with a FS 540 spin.',null,'https://youtu.be/r6hcjIbrbr8?t=236','NEVERMIND','EXPOSURE'),
  ('NH BS 180 Backflip',null,'8',now(),'2024-01-01','Sebastian Egger','180 Backflip but without using your hands',null,'https://youtu.be/r6hcjIbrbr8?t=263','STAND','STAND'),
  ('Rewind Yo-Yo','Leash Rewind to Rocket Mount','8',now(),'2025-01-01','Sebastian Egger','You drop to a leashfall and in the bottom of the bounce you wind yourself up in the leash then unwind again and use the momentum to get back up to the line. Finish in Expo.','You should probably wear a cup to protect your genitals (males and females!).
Having a shorter leash for this trick helps.','https://youtu.be/r6hcjIbrbr8?t=281','LEASH','EXPOSURE'),
  ('Reverse Rewind Yo-Yo','Leash Rewind to Reverse Rocket Mount','9',now(),'2024-01-01','Sebastian Egger','Drop to a leashfall and in the bottom of the bounce you wind yourself up in the leash, then unwind again and use the momentum to get back up to the line. Finish with a Reverse Rocket Mount.','You should probably wear a cup to protect your genitals (males and females!).
A short leash helps for this trick.','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r6hcjIbrbr8&t=300s','LEASH','EXPOSURE'),
  ('Robinspin','Triple Can of Soup','9',now(),'2025-01-01','Jordan Robinson','Three rolls from soup to standing in one bounce.','Doing the trick chongo-style with a down leg for all three rotations lets you use that leg to huck each time you come around.','https://www.youtube.com/shorts/Zch-UMRZAhc','SOUP','STAND'),
  ('Korean 180',null,'1',now(),null,null,'From Korean grab the line with both hands in front of you. Towards the top of the bounce swing one leg over the line so that you end up in the belly position. Then swing the other leg over the line so that you are back in Korean, only facing the other direction this time.','If it is hard to get the first leg over the line, try starting later in the bounce;As a preexercise you can practice the transition from Korean to Belly and vice verse in isolation before putting them together;','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3GWR5ZzSRBg','KOREAN','KOREAN'),
  ('Sick Nasty 180',null,'TBD',now(),null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
